{"tid":553172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國獵犬困橡樹幹監生餓死　天然風乾變木乃伊","createTime":"2018-02-07T07:57:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-07T11:10:55.000Z","uid":75969,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"84120166ac16b92516065445ff7421ff22d98020","tid":553172,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T07:57:41.000Z","msg":"圖喺下面<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在美國喬治亞州一個森林為主題的博物館內，最受歡迎的展品並不是珍稀的林木或樹葉，而是一具藏在橡樹樹幹內、面目猙獰的獵犬木乃伊。從獵犬絕望失焦的眼神，可想像到牠多年前被困樹身，慘遭活活餓死的景象。<br />\n<br />\n被命名為「小塞」（Stuckie）的木乃伊，現時被置放在南方森林世界（Southern Forest World）的一個展館內，每天都吸引到大批遊人探訪。伐木工人20多年前斬樹時，在橡樹中發現已成乾屍的「小塞」，大感錯愕，把牠送到博物館。<br />\n<br />\n博物館專家估計，「小塞」當年攀上高逾8.5米的橡樹追捕獵物時，不慎被困樹幹。樹幹內的空氣向上升帶走「小塞」遺體發出的氣味，令昆蟲等未有肆意蠶食身體；而且樹幹內極為乾燥，產出的丹寧酸亦有助風乾「小塞」的身體。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180207/photo/bknint-20180207101917265-0207_17011_001_01p.jpg?20180207130022\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180207%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20180207101917265-0207_17011_001_01p.jpg%3F20180207130022&h=fbab4a2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「小塞」現時被置放在南方森林世界。（互聯網圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180207/photo/bknint-20180207101917265-0207_17011_001_02b.jpg?20180207130022\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180207%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20180207101917265-0207_17011_001_02b.jpg%3F20180207130022&h=4f51b6a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「小塞」每天都吸引到大批遊人探訪。（互聯網圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180207/bknint-20180207101917265-0207_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180207%2Fbknint-20180207101917265-0207_17011_001.html&d=y%2Bec4sQHKQqngYfow8DPRE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=2f466b1f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180207/bknint-20180207101917265-0207_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d71013610802be247b16809f5747880311f7e64b","tid":553172,"uid":16061,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T07:59:20.000Z","msg":"變咗藝術品"},{"pid":"dfadd20b59f5dcba37dc4c7c8cded578dc6e4c5a","tid":553172,"uid":36178,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T08:04:27.000Z","msg":"好撚假喎"},{"pid":"26c74c95115d3fe1f5a6210bf525506d302326d9","tid":553172,"uid":16270,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"dfadd20b59f5dcba37dc4c7c8cded578dc6e4c5a","tid":553172,"uid":36178,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T08:04:27.000Z","msg":"好撚假喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T08:07:04.000Z","msg":"要有崩帶先真？"},{"pid":"6dbdf4a9435b784951f2219967290650c84dce44","tid":553172,"uid":28619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T08:23:50.000Z","msg":"有咩咁好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79fd67fb053ea9f9fefcf5ef376286c1d7557998","tid":553172,"uid":4166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T08:28:46.000Z","msg":"監生俾人塞入去當藝術品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09514063deac2324754bb9d39ce1f23ec3f516cb","tid":553172,"uid":46464,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T08:44:38.000Z","msg":"老衲死得好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c310b4cc097377302a651762e3e2b71cb7fafde","tid":553172,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T10:15:53.000Z","msg":"果度冇雨落架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d578ec3cb5bd2b27333c78310e2f09abeedcdd09","tid":553172,"uid":7436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T10